Another IPTV Player
===================

A free, open-source IPTV player for Xtream Codes and M3U/M3U8 playlists —
live TV, movies, and series. No analytics, no telemetry.

Not an IPTV provider: it hosts, sells, and distributes nothing.
Bring your own compatible service. The app is being rewritten as native
clients per platform; the original Flutter app is deprecated.


Features
--------

* Sources       — Xtream Codes and M3U/M3U8 (URL or file); multiple playlists.
* Content       — live TV, movies, series with rich detail views, search,
                  recently added.
* Playback      — mpv engine: HDR tone-mapping, PiP, background audio, offline
                  downloads, continue watching, auto play next, gestures,
                  aspect-ratio modes.
* Tracks & subs — per-item video/audio/subtitle memory; subtitle styling,
                  timing offset, external .srt.
* Organization  — favorites, resumable history, parental controls, hidden
                  categories, stats.
* App           — 10+ languages, no ads, no tracking.


Getting Started
---------------

1. Grab the latest build for your platform:
   https://github.com/bsogulcan/another-iptv-player/releases
2. Install and launch.
3. Add your provider credentials (URL, username, password) or an M3U playlist.


